ZH: 我们需负责任地对待我们的行为。
EN: We need to be responsible in our actions.

ZH: 这次会议需全体员工参加。
EN: All employees need to attend this meeting.

ZH: 你的建议是十分需的。
EN: Your suggestion is very much needed.

ZH: 为了完成这个任务，我们需更多的时间。
EN: We need more time to complete this task.

ZH: 我们需确保所有工作都按时完成。
EN: We need to ensure that all the tasks are completed on time.

ZH: 在这个项目中，我们需高度合作。
EN: In this project, we need to collaborate closely.

ZH: 这是一个紧急情况，我们需立即采取行动。
EN: This is an emergency situation, we need to take action immediately.

ZH: 我们需向客户提供高质量的服务。
EN: We need to provide high-quality service to our customers.

ZH: 这是我们产品的需市场。
EN: This is the market demand for our product.

ZH: 我们应该根据需来管理我们的资源。
EN: We should manage our resources based on demand.

ZH: 这份工作需要一些特定的技能，你需具备。
EN: This job requires some specific skills that you need to have.

ZH: 你需按照老师的指示完成这个作业。
EN: You need to complete this assignment according to the teacher's instructions.

ZH: 为了取得成功，我们需付出更多的努力。
EN: In order to achieve success, we need to put in more effort.

ZH: 我们的产品需满足客户的需求。
EN: Our products need to meet the needs of our customers.

ZH: 这个问题需了解更多的信息才能得出结论。
EN: We need to gather more information to draw a conclusion on this issue.

ZH: 为了提高生产效率，我们需引入新的技术。
EN: To improve productivity, we need to introduce new technologies.

ZH: 他的观点是建立在客观需上的。
EN: His opinion is based on objective needs.

ZH: 我们需清楚地了解市场需求。
EN: We need to have a clear understanding of market demands.

ZH: 她需时时刻刻保持专注。
EN: She needs to stay focused at all times.

ZH: 我们需与供应商建立长期的合作关系。
EN: We need to establish long-term partnerships with suppliers.
